Green_Bay.Oneida Golf and Country Club:
Oneida Golf and Country Club, often simply just called Oneida, is a country club located in Green Bay, Wisconsin. Established in 1928, this club has both a pool and tennis area as well as a golf course.


== Golf Course ==
Oneida Golf and Country Club is the leading private, member owned golf club in northeastern WI. Established in 1928, we are a full service private club by membership only.
